aths, and copy those bin files over to the Debug directory.<br><br>Run it with this to start:&nbsp; &quot;mpiexec -n 1 helloworldMPI.exe&quot;.&nbsp; Then change the -n 1 to -n x where x is the number of cores you have.&nbsp; Say yes to allowing mpiexec firewall access if that comes up.<br><br>If this bombs out, there's something wrong on your machine.<br><br>Damien<o:p></o:p></p></div><p class=MsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p></div></DIV></BODY></HTML>

